{"tid":1189704,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實只要奶共達D護主犬肯認主人奶共,件事就可以好快告一段落","createTime":"2019-06-07T02:17:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-07T02:27:44.000Z","uid":49197,"like":5,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ba2a8c2154dedc1e824240af6c31c07d2a98fb4d","tid":1189704,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:17:11.000Z","msg":"奶共達以前的確講過「導人向善,改變世界」「雞蛋同高牆,永遠企喺雞蛋果面」去呃like<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但之後幫支那寶賣廣告、講蝗語、用簡體字打機,佢近年不斷幫支那文化侵略香港,已經唔係以前果個達哥、達叔,所以成件事已經唔係咩中唔中立、表唔表態咁簡單,而係佢直頭有份幫中共手出賣香港人</span></span></strong>,但班達狗粉一見倒有人指出達狗賣港既事實,就發晒矛咁空群而出護主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實佢幫手文化侵略香港,有份賣港,你地咪認囉,成日想收兩家茶禮兩邊都唔得失,有無咁著數呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日期：6月9日（日）<br />\n集合地點：銅鑼灣東角道<br />\n時間：下午2時30分集合，3時正起步<br />\n遊行路線：銅鑼灣東角道遊行至金鐘添美道立法會<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-Qrymc2mYHlY/UPDKs5emWdI/AAAAAAAADpc/WblPdCbA6I4/s1600/%E4%B9%A0%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%B6%E6%97%8F%E5%A4%9A%E7%A7%BB%E6%B0%91%E5%A4%96%E5%9B%BD.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-Qrymc2mYHlY%2FUPDKs5emWdI%2FAAAAAAAADpc%2FWblPdCbA6I4%2Fs1600%2F%25E4%25B9%25A0%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E6%2597%258F%25E5%25A4%259A%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E6%25B0%2591%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%259B%25BD.JPG&h=a615823d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"89ca9e82294dfca84daeb8f3bacfc11d2e196aa9","tid":1189704,"uid":249971,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-07T02:18:45.000Z","msg":"因達哥而分裂，係助長緊五毛<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1189127\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1189127</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b5b887b9a7413182bbb8386ee4212eb2a8163d3f","tid":1189704,"uid":49197,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"89ca9e82294dfca84daeb